SOLARIS-SYS-MONITOR TESTS
-----------
Tests that verify "Solaris Performance Monitor" functionality.

Safety
------
These tests will not change any configurations on test machine, they are safe to run.


Configuration
-------------
No configuration is needed

Version
-------
Tests were updated for Solaris11 and its update release

Available Testsuites
--------------------
* To verify the information listed in first System tab
* To verify the Processes table will change its contents view according to different process view conditions
* To verify the information listed in Resources tab
* To verify open/close preferences dialog will not affect application itself
